trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> class acts as a page catalog to maintain any controls previously added to the page that a user has closed, so that the user can add them back to the page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>klassen fungerer som en siden katalog å beholde alle kontroller har lagt til siden som en bruker har avsluttet, slik at brukeren kan legge dem tilbake til siden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: This control is visible only when a Web page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: Denne kontrollen vises bare når en webside er i visningsmodus for katalogen.

trans-unit.source: The PageCatalogPartDesigner class provides design-time support for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> class.
trans-unit.target: Klassen PageCatalogPartDesigner gir støtte for utforming for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning markup kildekode som beskriver den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPartDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPartDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the HTML that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter HTML som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The HTML markup used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: HTML-koden brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Forbereder utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"> </xref> kontrollen.
